t/uploads/2023/10/Drake-and-Michael-Jackson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Drake-and-Michael-Jackson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Drake-and-Michael-Jackson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Drake-and-Michael-Jackson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/drake">德雷克</a>(Drake) 和<a href="/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊 (Michael Jackson)</a>并列<em>公告牌</em>历史上单曲排行榜第一名最多的男性歌手。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-for-all-the-dogs-review-tracklist-lyrics-3511670">德雷克（Drake）——《为了所有的狗》评论：无暴力、苦涩、深沉的中度</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位说唱歌手与<a href="/artists/j-cole">J. Cole</a>合作的歌曲《First Person Shooter》首次登上<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/drake-top-three-hot-100-debuts-whats-next-number-one/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em> Hot 100</a>排行榜第一名，成为他在美国排行榜上的第 13 首冠军歌曲，这是自杰克逊复出以来尚未被超越的记录1995 年。（根据<a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/drake-gets-no-1-album-and-single-tying-michael-jackson-for-billboard-hot-100-record/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork</em></a> ）</p><p>两位音乐家现在并列，在热门 100 强排行榜上排名第四。披头士乐队目前以 20 首歌曲占据排行榜第一名，紧随其后的是玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey)，有 19 首上榜歌曲，雷安娜 (Rhianna) 紧随其后。落后14。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Drake - 第一人称射击游戏（音频）ft. J. Cole" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sRs2o36a1Us?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>讽刺的是，《第一人称射击》的歌词预示了德雷克说唱的里程碑： <em>“我距离迈克尔只有一步之遥”</em> ，并暗指杰克逊 1982 年的标志性热门单曲《Beat It》。 The track also marks Cole&#39;s first Hot 100 Number One track.</p><p> The song is featured on Drake&#39;s eighth studio album &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-bets-850k-on-logan-paul-to-beat-dillon-danis-via-ko-3514846">For All The Dogs</a> &#39;. The LP also earned the top spot on the <em>Billboard</em> 200 chart making it the rapper&#39;s 13th Number One album. Per <a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/drake-for-all-the-dogs-album-number-one-billboard-200-chart-1235442875/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a> <em>,</em> the LP earned the equivalent of 402,000 units, with the overwhelming majority of them due to streaming: 391,000 units compared to 10,000 album sale units.</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-bets-850k-on-logan-paul-to-beat-dillon-danis-via-ko-3514846">two-star review of &#39;For All The Dogs&#39;</a> , <em>NME</em> shared:“Trailed as a return to form, the rap megastar instead doubles-down on his worst impulses on the final album before his health-induced hiatus.”</p><p> It continued: “&#39;For All The Dogs&#39;- his third solo LP in as many years – not only feels tiring, but sounds tired too.”</p><p> Elsewhere, Drake&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-six-year-old-son-adonis-debut-single-my-man-freestyle-3515443">six-year-old son, Adonis Graham, recently released a debut single</a> titled &#39;My Man Freestyle&#39;.</p><p> Produced by Lil E$$o, the song is an extended version of Adonis&#39; brief verse on &#39;Daylight&#39;.在这首俏皮的歌曲中，我们看到了关于<i>“在我的 iPad 上玩”</i>和<i>“向我爸爸打招呼”的新兴 MC 说唱。</i></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-ties-michael-jackson-for-most-number-one-hits-by-a-male-solo-artist-3518073">Drake ties Michael Jackson for most Number One hits by a male solo artist</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
